                             <h2><a href="http://texascitycomputerrepair.com/what-is-required-for-you-to-become-a-computer-technician/">What Is Required For You To Become A Computer Technician?</a></h2>
                           	
            <div class="entry-content">
            			
               <p>In our last article, we talked about the pestering question on every techs mind when getting started.Â <a href="http://texascitycomputerrepair.com/is-a-business-license-required-to-be-a-computer-repair-technician/">Do IÂ need a business license for computer repair</a></p>
<p>Now we&#8217;ll dig a bit deeper&#8230; Computer repair technicians are called upon all the time, by homeowners and businesses. If you want to take on this profession, you need to know the typical duties that are required and understand that an extensive knowledge base is also required. You better think about schooling and all kinds of training courses and certifications if you plan to go into business as a computer tech. You might be thinking about the self-taught approach. However, even if you were able to learn everything and get the experience you need, you&#8217;re going to be dealing with customers that are looking for certified and licensed technicians.</p>
