                             <h2><a href="http://texascitycomputerrepair.com/is-a-business-license-required-to-be-a-computer-repair-technician/">Is A Business License Required To Be A Computer Repair Technician?</a></h2>
                           	
            <div class="entry-content">
            			
               <p>I would assume if I were to become a computer repair technician that a business license would be required. I&#8217;m sure some people try to get away with not having a business license for such a practice. For example, there are people that operate out of their own home. However, it would be safe to say that legally, a business license would be expected. Not only that, but I would think that you need to be licensed and certified as a computer repair technician in general. It never pays to take the shortcuts out there, so make sure you get that business license.</p>
            </div>
             
                    </div>
    </div>
    </div>

